			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Well i got to thinking today and was wondering can our dodge go past 170?  Or is it hardcapped for us at 170?  There is a few %dodge augments and wondering if it would be a good investment hehe.  I know monks can go as high as 230 in dodge.  Any info would be great =).  </span></td>
